	   <tr><td colspan=2>After careful consideration, I've decided to follow the path of a Troll Shadow Knight. However, I'm not sure what deity I should worship - Innoruuk or Cazic-Thule. Could anyone please point out the specific advantages and disadvantages the two deities have over each other, gameplay-wise?<br><br>Thank you in advance.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
