<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=103620161969712></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f103620161969712><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=5&mid=103620161969712>RE: Who to worship?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=5&mid=103620161969712#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=84469><span id=Sage>ZifnabFan</span></a>, <span id=Sage>Sage</span><br><span id=notbold>102 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Nov 1st 9:07 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.95]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Really depends who you see yourself hanging with more for 'un'church on EQ sundays.<br><br>Ogres, Iksars, Erudites, and I believe Gnomes are more then likely (actaully 100% likely in some cases, it's their only choice) worshipping Cazic.<br><br>Your Humans and Dark Elves are more likely worshipping Innoruuk (although the former is just what i've seen, players can choose either)<br><br>That, and the which do you like more, hate or fear, seem to be it. I agree with the other posters. Very little differance in what you'll use gear wise, both sides have strong points.<br><br>Personally i'd say Fear, just because i see Troll SK's as being very much into digging folks being very, very, very afraid of them over just hating stuff. To me hate is more of a human/dark elf reason, or maybe gnomish. Plus ogres and trolls to me are closer then trolls/dark elves, so i just see troll's worshipping like their ogre buddies do. Thats me though and an entirely RP decision. yours is gonna have to be up to you<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
