	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hands down Rangers are the best soloers. Of all the melees, only three can solo in high levels, Rangers, SKs &amp; Bards because these classes can kite. Of the hybrids, only two can solo, Rangers and SKs. Pallies can't solo. <br><br>#1) Rangers: Have the best snare, can fear all animals and can kill mobs the fastest of all hybrids.<br><br>#2) Shadow Knights: Have Darkness spells but will not slow a mob as good as snare, breaks too early, and has long casting time but however can fear all mobs.<br><br>#3) Paladins: Can't solo. Has fear against undead but no snare spell.<br><br>51st Shadow Knight<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
