mp;#8217;t know; don&amp;#8217;t play either of those classes.  =).  As far as being easy for a 60, heh, probably wouldn&amp;#8217;t go that far.  I have a 60 DE SK friend that was reasonably equipped fail the first couple of times he tried.  He a wimp for a group, but a decent to good challenge for a solo person.  A SK soloing a ravishing in DL is a far cry from an SK soloing Yeldevra in WW, even factoring in the level difference.<br><br>Root was only brought up as another way a RGR can solo.  I didn&amp;#8217;t really make too much a point of it; guess Im shocked you are asking about it.  =)<br><br>Also, I apologize if my message came across as attacking or anything.  If it did, I didn&amp;#8217;t effectively communicate.  I was merely challenging your statements, not saying they were right or wrong (for the most part), or anything else derogatory.  Just wanted clarification  =)<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
